title: AccountsLegend

comments.body: Since you don't want "fake people", maybe you should share what is it all about, what are those tasks that people will have to do.

comments.author: stompix
comments.body: Quote from: Rikafip on January 18, 2023, 11:30:53 AMSince you don't want "fake people", maybe you should share what is it all about, what are those tasks that people will have to do.I have a feeling he is not going to do so as he knows he will be criticized for the task, if it was a simple thing that could be done with no problem he would have already said, 5$ to do this, as he said in some of his other "offers", but since he says real it will most likely have something to do with your identity, so far better to stay away from such deals, most of them will come to bite you in the ass later.
